en_9621848_1	The ceremony, which will see 180 projects vested in the public will go on for a period of 3 days commencing from today (August 01).
en_9621848_2	A new building for the Divulankadawala Central College in Medirigiriya was handed over to the students today (August 01).
en_9621848_3	Addressing those gathered the President stated that every district has been divided to ensure balanced development and that we don’t look into our parents’ wellbeing enough.
